 As a real scoop as a small mid-sized car, Seat offers lighting on this Leon Full LED. 

00:04:01.349 --> 00:04:05.299
 Only on the more expensive models. But we can show it on this FR. 

00:04:05.299 --> 00:04:09.049
 Today we actually ride a kind of sheep in wolf's clothes. 

00:04:09.049 --> 00:04:11.719
 The exterior is completely sporty and FR. 

00:04:11.719 --> 00:04:16.069
 And inside is the smallest 1.4-liter TSI petrol engine 

00:04:16.069 --> 00:04:17.789
 with 122 hp. 

00:04:17.789 --> 00:04:22.710
 Only in 2013 there will also be a smaller 1.2 TSI with 90 or 105 hp 

00:04:22.710 --> 00:04:25.810
 and then of course also come much stronger gasoline engines that really fit this appearance. 

00:04:25.810 --> 00:04:30.030
 The smallest diesel version will be a 1.6 TDI with 90 hp. 

