 The conclusion could be that the new Leon is just as expensive as a Golf 

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:51.469
 But that's not true 

00:04:51.469 --> 00:04:54.819
 because for the money of a three-door Golf you get a five-door Leon, standard. 

